#SYMBOL_NAME "Lockton Restroom Logic v1.0"
#CATEGORY "46"
#DEFAULT_VOLATILE
#ENABLE_STACK_CHECKING

#HELP_BEGIN
Project-Specific Logic for Restrooms
------------------------------------
This module serves as a logic placeholder/stub for the 9th and 10th floor 
restroom audio zones. 

Currently, it only initializes the 'Logic_Ready' flag to allow the Break 
Room UI to boot. Future development will expand this module to orchestrate 
Sonos volume syncing, zone muting, and touch panel admin lockouts for the 
restroom speakers without cluttering the main Break Room logic file.
#HELP_END

DIGITAL_OUTPUT Logic_Ready;

Function Main()
{
    WaitForInitializationComplete();
    Logic_Ready = 1;
}
